    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of a rough idle when cold. The exterior has a few noticeable scratches and minor door dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear on the driver's seat. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind a few imperfections.",
