    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This fantastic ride is in good condition and has been well-loved! It runs smoothly and looks great, showing only the typical minor wear you'd expect from a car that\u2019s been enjoyed and cared for. It's a reliable, solid choice that\u2019s ready to hit the road today!",
