    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no scratches, dings, or imperfections to be found anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no pending maintenance needs. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model that looks and drives like new.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
